reviewText:
Same stuff you see on TV.  All one sided view of law enforcement.  If you want to see a better movie,
see "Dead in 5 Heartbeats", presented by Sonny Barger.

If you believe the primary purpose of joining a motorcycle club is to sell drugs and kill other bikers and you don't mind hearing the same 3 songs over and over, then this is the documentary for you. Not recommended for those prone to epilepsy triggered by the constant bright flashes or who get bored hearing the same parts of the story repeated over and over again.
Really enjoyed it! Vast majority of the video occurs in Canada.
